data.text:
PARKING UPDATE

Due to ongoing construction, the parking lot north of the Cathedral office on Logan Street is no longer available. The parking lot just south of the Cathedral office on Logan Street is free for Saturday vigil Mass and all Sunday Masses.

We also have a free parking lot on Pennsylvania Street, on the east side of the Cathedral.

CATHEDRAL BASILICA PARKING

Parking is available every day in the Mary Garden

Parking Lot at Colfax and Pennsylvania.

If that lot is full, parking is on the street or in the area pay parking lots.

On Saturday and Sunday, for Masses only, parking is free in the two parking lots on Logan Street on either side of the red brick office building.

Other times, those are pay lots.
